						<summary>

						<p>Incomplete. This inscription records a gift of money (<hi rend="italic">4 paḻañjalāgai achchu</hi>) probably for offering sandal paste by one of the saints namely Namaśivāyar who deposited the amount with the priests (<hi rend="italic">Śivabrāhamanas</hi>) of the temple named Sīgāḻi and Avināsimurugaṉ.</p>						

